'''''Dragon Fin Soup''''' is a [[role-playing video game]] created by the independent development studio Grimm Bros. The game is the studio's first title. It is influenced by [[roguelike]] games and uses procedural generation for parts of the game. The game has two modes: Story mode follows a story and is more like a typical RPG, while Survival mode skips the story and focuses on the surviving within the game and constrains players with [[permadeath]]<U+2014>once the player character dies, the game must be restarted from the beginning.<ref>{{cite news|title=Dragon Fin Soup is an RPG with a roguelike garnish|url=http://www.vg247.com/2014/03/19/dragon-fin-soup-is-an-rpg-with-a-roguelike-garnish/|first=Mike|last=Irving|date=Mar 19, 2014|work=[[VG247]]|accessdate=Mar 25, 2014}}</ref>

